des:
Simply ask Alexa to control your Humax products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download the Humax Smart Living app from the app store then register an account (or log in if you already have one);
2. Configure your devices in the Humax Smart Living app and rename appropriately (e.g. living room light);
3. Enable the “Humax Smart Living” skill on the Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Setup is complete. Enjoy voice control on your home devices using commands such as:
Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.
Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.
Alexa, turn on the living room TV.
Alexa, turn off the living room TV.
